org.hps.record.evio

Enum EvioBankTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EvioBankTag>
      • org.hps.record.evio.EvioBankTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EvioBankTag>

    public enum EvioBankTag
extends Enum<EvioBankTag>
    Convenience enum for representing bank tag values in HPS-formatted EVIO events.

    Documentation of the bank tags and contents can be found at
    EVIO Data Format.
